Acts ch. 376, sec. 10, effective July 15, 1988; and ch. 394, sec. 1, effective July 15, 1988. -- Amended 1986 Ky. Acts ch. 214, sec. 9, effective July 15, 1986; and ch. 296, sec. 9, effective July 15, 1986. -- Amended 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 379, sec. 8, effective April 9, 1982. -- Amended 1978 Ky.
